    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS. This chassis remains rigid with documented subframe reinforcement already completed. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. Recent comprehensive service includes a full valve adjustment and preventative rod bearing replacement, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is met with mechanical integrity. The suspension features upgraded polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in response and minimized deflection. A mechanically robust example optimized for performance-oriented ownership.",
      "price": 34500.0,
