    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior paint retains a beautiful, deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you will find minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch consistent with standard use. The interior is smoke-free and features premium leather seating that remains firm and comfortable, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronics, including the dual-zone climate control and the premium infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it comes with a complete service logbook, a fresh oil change, and the brake pads were replaced just 3,000 miles ago. The engine runs smoothly without any leaks or unusual noises, and the transmission shifts crisply. It is a reliable, honest car that is ready for its next owner.",
